      "weather": "FINE",
      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HEART TO HARTLEY (2) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 4 lengths at this track in a handy 17.82 beating Fabulous Fleur. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Has hit winning form and can go on with it. SHIRL THE WHIRL (1) was checked in the run and safely held when fourth (18.44) in a TG1-4W over 305m at this track. Can do much better this time. COMPTON BLUE (7) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (23.77) at this track behind Extravagantly in a TG1-4W. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Hard to beat again. SHANNY ROSE (8) gets a chance to redeem an unplaced effort here last start.",
